  "title": "Assistant manager",
  "description": "<p>Roles & Responsibilities</p><ul><li><strong>Job Requirement</strong></li><li>Provide excellent customer service, product knowledge and recommendations to customers</li><li>Preparation of Ingredients, Tea brewing accordingly to SOP</li><li>Assist in inventory management and stock take</li><li>Maintain housekeeping of the store; ensuring cleanliness and organize store front</li><li>Maintain and manage the POS/Cashier</li><li>Assist in ad-hoc job scope assigned by store manager</li><li>Training is provided</li><li>Fresh graduate are welcome</li><li>Possess excellent communication skills with a friendly and helpful demeanor</li><li>Willing to work a flexible schedule including morning, afternoon, weekends and holidays in a fast paced and dynamic environment</li><li>Aspiring to grow your career internationally</li><li>Full Time & Part Time positions available (Able to commit at least 4-6 months (for part-timers)</li><li>read and speak chinese is a must as the menu consist of chinese</li><li>Address: OUTLETS ISLAND WIDE</li></ul>",
